CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Expensify Inc is a cloud-based expense management software platform that helps the smallest to the largest businesses simplify the way they manage money. More than 10 million people use Expensify's free features, which include corporate cards, expense tracking, next-day reimbursement, invoicing, bill pay, and travel booking in one app.
